OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,8,Fspoken with her US counterpart, as
OL,9,FDonald Trump faced condemnation after
OL,10,Fwarning "a whole civilisation will
OL,11,Fdie" if Iran failed to meet his
OL,12,Fdeadline to reopen the Strait of
OL,13,FHormuz.
OL,15,FThe escalating crisis in the Middle
OL,16,FEast and apocalyptic rhetoric has seen
OL,17,Fthe White House reject claims it would
OL,18,Fuse nuclear weapons against Tehran.
OL,26,@rD@IOUsD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
