FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FThe US president had given Tehran
OL,8,Funtil 1am on Wednesday UK time to end
OL,9,Fits chokehold on the strait or face
OL,10,Fannihilation.
OL,12,FMr Trump has said the US will destroy
OL,13,FIran's bridges and power stations as
OL,14,Fhe brushed off concerns attacks on
OL,15,Fcivilian infrastructure could
OL,16,Fconstitute a war crime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FIn the face of ongoing military
OL,8,Fstrikes by the US and Israel, Iran has
OL,9,Ftightened its grip on the critical
OL,10,Fshipping route, sending global oil and
OL,11,Fgas prices skyrocketing and causing
OL,12,Fglobal economic uncertainty.
OL,14,FAs the clock ticked down on Mr Trump's
OL,15,Fultimatum, strikes on Iran intensified
OL,16,Fwith attacks on Kharg Island, the
OL,17,Fcountry's main oil export terminal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FIn a speech in Hungary, vice president
OL,8,FJD Vance said the US has "tools in our
OL,9,Ftoolkit that we so far haven't decided
OL,10,Fto use".
OL,12,FHe added: "The president of the United
OL,13,FStates can decide to use them and he
OL,14,Fwill decide to use them if the
OL,15,FIranians don't change their course of
OL,16,Fconduct."
OL,18,FThis was seized on by critics on
OL,19,Fsocial media, who said it implied Mr
OL,20,FTrump "might use nuclear weapons".
OL,26,@pD@ZOUrD@GO]tD@KOUxD@IO]|D@GOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FBut hitting back, the White House's
OL,8,Fofficial rapid response account on X
OL,9,Fsaid: "Literally nothing @VP said here
OL,10,F'implies' this, you absolute buffoons."
OL,12,FHowever, when asked about the use of
OL,13,Fnuclear weapons, White House press
OL,14,Fsecretary Karoline Leavitt restated
OL,15,Fthe upcoming deadline and added: "Only
OL,16,Fthe president knows where things stand
OL,17,Fand what he will do."
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@gO]wD@bOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FEarlier, writing on his Truth Social
OL,8,Fplatform, Mr Trump said: "A whole
OL,9,Fcivilisation will die tonight, never
OL,10,Fto be brought back again.
OL,12,F"I don't want that to happen, but it
OL,13,Fprobably will."
OL,15,FAmong those to criticise his ominous
OL,16,Fthreat was Pope Leo XIV, who branded
OL,17,Fit "truly unacceptable".
OL,26,@pD@ZOUtD@AOUuD@OO]yD@DOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
