PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FMeanwhile, frantic diplomatic efforts
OL,8,Fare continuing to seek an end to
OL,9,Fhostilities, with Pakistan, which has
OL,10,Facted as a mediator between the
OL,11,Fwarring sides, calling on Mr Trump to
OL,12,Fextend his deadline on Iran by a
OL,13,Ffurther two weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
