PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FSeparately, the US State Department
OL,8,Fsaid secretary of state Marco Rubio
OL,9,Fand Ms Cooper had spoken "about the
OL,10,FIranian regime's ongoing attacks
OL,11,Facross the Middle East and the
OL,12,Fcritical importance of restoring
OL,13,Ffreedom of navigation in the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz".
OL,16,FA spokesman added: "The secretary and
OL,17,FForeign Secretary agreed on the need
OL,18,Ffor international efforts to ensure
OL,19,Fshipping can move freely and energy
OL,20,Fsupplies can reach global markets."
OL,26,@qD@ZOUvD@GO]xD@TOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
