FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, the UK chaired a meeting
OL,8,Fof military planners from a coalition
OL,9,Fof more than 30 nations examining long-
OL,10,Fterm measures to make the shipping
OL,11,Froute safe and accessible once
OL,12,Fhostilities have ended.
OL,14,FHowever, a move at the United Nations
OL,15,Fin New York to safeguard commercial
OL,16,Fvessels in the maritime pinchpoint was
OL,17,Fdealt a blow after it was vetoed by
OL,18,FRussia and China.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FArchie Young, the UK's deputy
OL,8,Fpermanent representative to the UN,
OL,9,Fsaid: "No country should be allowed to
OL,10,Fhold the world economy hostage. Yet
OL,11,Fthat is exactly what Iran is doing by
OL,12,Fdenying the right of transit passage,
OL,13,Fa key navigational right under
OL,14,Finternational law."
OL,16,FHe added: "Today, Russia and China
OL,17,Fchose to shield their ally Iran rather
OL,18,Fthan join international efforts to
OL,19,Fopen the strait and avert risks to the
OL,20,Fglobal economy."
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@SO]xD@KOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775624629
OL,3,CTransatlantic crisis talks as Trump
OL,4,Ccondemned for Iran deadline wipeout
OL,5,Cthreat
OL,7,FHe went on: "It is Iran's actions that
OL,8,Fhave closed the strait. This has
OL,9,Falready had dire consequences and the
OL,10,Flonger this stranglehold continues the
OL,11,Fworse the situation will get.
OL,13,FMr Young said it was "deeply
OL,14,Fregrettable" the resolution proposed
OL,15,Fby Bahrain did not pass.
OL,26,@oD@MOUuD@VOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
